data.description: Welcome to 4920 Wynship Ln, where hidden potential awaits within this diamond in the rough! This home features a touch of luxury with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances in the kitchen. The spacious family room boasts high trey ceilings, creating an inviting and open atmosphere. While the home may not be currently organized or clean, envision the possibilities that lie beneath the surface. After a good cleaning, this property is poised to showcase its true beauty. Don't miss the chance to transform this space into your dream home, combining elegant features with the untapped potential within. Schedule a showing today to explore the hidden charm of this 3-bed, 2-bath Ranch. Discover the allure of this property and imagine the stunning transformation that awaits!
